data.description: Location! Well maintained end unit with garage and recent updates! Luxury Vinyl flooring and tastefully painted throughout the first level. Spacious living area with direct vent fireplace, adjacent eating/dining space and a sliding glass door to the back that brings in tons of natural light! White and bright kitchen. Half bath on the first floor. 2 bedrooms and 2 remodeled full baths upstairs. The Blendon Park Community includes a pool, fitness center, and clubhouse. The HOA fee includes water, trash, sewer, lawn, snow removal, exterior maintenance & insurance. Walking distance to Blendon Woods Metro Park, and very close to restaurants, shopping, and 161/270. Move-in ready!
